<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="within-prep">within <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɪ'ðɪn/    美 /wɪ'ðɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在...范围 / 时间以内；不超过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I completed the task within 40 minutes.
我在40分钟内完成了任务。</p><footer>2015重庆</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Put the tools <strong>within</strong> your <strong>reach</strong>.
把工具放在你能够得着的地方。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Should they keep their conclusion within the team or share it with other employees? 
他们是应该将结论保留在团队内，还是与其他员工分享？</p><footer>2011 浙江</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It saves time in the kitchen to have things you use a lot <strong><em>_</em></strong>_easy reach.   （2009 山东改）<br />
A.near<br />
B.upon<br />
D.around  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. within   </p></div>